    Parallel-plate submicron gap formed by micromachined low-density pillars for near-field radiative heat transfer

Appl. Phys. Lett. 106 , 083504 (2015); https://doi.org/10.1063/1.4913692
Kota Ito 1,2 , a) , Atsushi Miura 1 , Hideo Iizuka 1 , and Hiroshi Toshiyoshi 2
more... View Affiliations
View Contributors

